summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, governing the location of adult cabarets and providing for termination of non-conforming adult cabaret uses, amending sections 23.47.004, 23.49.062, 23.49.118, 23.49.144, 23.49.320, 23.49.338, 23.50.012, 23.54.015, 23.66.122, 23.66.322, 23.84.006, and 23.84.030 of the Seattle Municipal (Land Use) Code, and adding Sections 23.49.027, and 23.50.019 to the Seattle Municipal (Land Use) Code.
